1.title: Kockout Delivery
1.plot: Two grandmas battle it out to the end as they stake their claim to their new grandson. One dad, who's really just a big kid at heart, is ecstatic to meet his new playmate. And, two high school sweethearts bring their third baby into the world.

2.title: The Rocky Road to Parenthood
2.plot: A recovering drug addict with a new lease on life has the opportunity to prove that he's a new man. Plus, after losing three babies in three years, an emotional couple faces a nerve-wracking delivery. And a couple that has no clue what they're doing can expect little help from their lively moms.

3.title: The Heart to Survive
3.plot: It's every parent's worst nightmare as this baby's first moments of life are a battle to survive. Then, an enormous fibroid proves to be a massive obstacle to delivery. And a two-time fainting father is once again in the eye of the storm.

4.title: My Wife's Cervix Is My Hero
4.plot: All eyes are on a couple that's desperately hoping for the safe arrival of their quadruplets. Then, a long-distance runner who expects her first delivery to be a walk in the park is in for the marathon of her life. And a preacher delivers his eighth baby with his own hands.

7.title: Graduating to Parenthood
7.plot: A teenage mom is left in a daze as her baby is rushed to the NICU moments after its first breath. And, a progressive couple is determined to go all natural in the delivery of their second baby. Plus, a stay-at-home dad gets a friendly lesson in Japanese tradition from his mother-in-law.

8.title: An Unexpected Delivery
8.plot: Two childhood sweethearts, who've endured a world of heartache in their journey to parenthood, finally have their dreams within reach. And, a first time mom who's done more than her fair share of research has no idea what's about to hit her. Plus, a couple that had the easiest delivery imaginable with their first baby is not getting off so easily this time around.

1.title: To Medicate or Not?
1.plot: From a woman who wants everything she can get for pain to a woman who doesn't even want it mentioned, every Mom must make their own decision on how to manage their labor pains.

2.title: Expect the Unexpected
2.plot: There's never a dull moment in Labor and Delivery. From the patients that you treat to the problems that you greet. Witness the most terrifying complication in Labor and Delivery and one of the most unusual patients ever...a mom pregnant with twins from two different fathers.

3.title: Who Is the Baby Now?
3.plot: A loving couple conquers the dreaded needle, only to face a gut-wrenching c-section. Two teenagers cram for the test of parenthood as they say goodbye to their childhood. And a first time mom tries to joke her way through delivery but it's her labor that gets the last laugh.

4.title: Mama Knows Best
4.plot: Their first delivery was disaster, but even a military tour in Iraq couldn't prepare him for this. She has three boys at home and is carrying her last baby, but her dreams of having a girl are replaced with hopes for her baby's survival. It's the first baby for these newlyweds and when her labor starts to drag on her mother has to step in.

5.title: Mission Impossible
5.plot: This self proclaimed type-A forgot her birth plan at home forcing her to rely on her primal instinct. This mom of four boys wants a girl and her parents are with her all the way but her delivery is way more than she bargained for.

6.title: Patience is the Name of the Game
6.plot: Go behind-the-scenes in a maternity ward as expectant mothers go through their last stage of pregnancy. From the front desk to the delivery room, our cameras captures high drama, emotion and incredible heart as new lives begin and others are changed forever.

7.title: Fear is a Four Letter Word
7.plot: Two sportscasters are taking their first shot at parenthood, but a nagging condition threatens their chances for glory. Twins are in store for this happy couple but her previous delivery has everyone on the edge of their seats. And all pregnant women experience a little fear, but this first time mom takes being scared really seriously.

imdb.plot outline: Series takes an in-depth look at life inside the maternity ward at Riverside Methodist Hospital in Columbus, Ohio, as expectant mothers enter their final stage of pregnancy. From the delivery room, to the operating room, to the front desk, to the nurses' station...40 cameras roll 24 hours a day, 7 days a week to capture the high drama, humor and overwhelming emotion of child birth as new lives begin and others change forever.
